<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="lightly-adv">lightly <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'laɪtli/    美 /'laɪtli/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>轻轻地；轻微地；少量地；轻率地：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>step in lightly 
轻轻地走进来</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>rain lightly
下小雨</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>This is not a problem we should <strong>take lightly</strong>.
这个问题我们可不能掉以轻心。</p></div></div>